    BuildingInput
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) class for transferring building data between the application's layers, such as from the service layer to the presentation layer or through RESTful APIs.

    Data Transfer Object (DTO) for conveying information about the association between buildings and goods, particularly focusing on the cost aspect.

    Data Transfer Object (DTO) for conveying good-related information between the application layers, particularly useful for transferring good data to and from the user interface or API endpoints.
